📜 Privacy Policy for Gizéy Dictionary App
Effective Date: April 16, 2025

Thank you for using the Gizéy Dictionary app. Your privacy is important to us. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information—especially regarding the use of your microphone.

🎤 Microphone Access (RECORD_AUDIO)
We request access to your device’s microphone only to allow you to record and contribute audio pronunciations of words to the dictionary.

We do not record any audio without your explicit action (you must tap a record button).

Audio recordings are used only within the app to improve the language resource.

We do not share, sell, or expose your audio data to third parties.

🛡️ Data Storage & Security
Audio contributions may be stored securely to support app functionality.

We follow modern security practices to protect your data.

You may request deletion of any audio you've contributed.

👤 No Personal Data Collection
We do not collect any personal data such as name, email, phone number, or location unless you explicitly provide it.

📬 Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us at:

Email: ihimbruzadolf@gmail.com

